findings.title: Out of gas exception if there will be a long excluded addresses list
findings.description: The function includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply uses loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the excluded addresses list is too long.
